Coffey v. Craven, Warden. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, Albert W. Harris, Jr., Assistant Attorney General, and Joyce Ferris Nedde, Deputy Attorney General, in opposition.

C. A. 9th Cir. Petition presented to Mr. Justice Douglas for reconsideration of denial of bail, and by him referred to the Court, denied.
